67435153\" width=606 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/8dcc517ec8e6f2bd76896b6f7d2e3403.webm?t=1767435153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/8dcc517ec8e6f2bd76896b6f7d2e3403.mp4?t=1767435153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not every constraint is explained. Use your deduction skills and assign meaning to these opaque constraints. All puzzles work as intended, please ignore any discrepancies or odd behavior from our Stips. It's fine. You're fine.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/37e121b89c6c3a77158caffd02aa7751.avif?t=1767435153\" width=617 height=97 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/b8df1978c65c6512725a22e8a44bc620.poster.avif?t=1767435153\" width=616 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/b8df1978c65c6512725a22e8a44bc620.webm?t=1767435153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227960/extras/b8df1978c65c6512725a22e8a44bc620.mp4?t=1767435153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stip's puzzles are connected in a series of rooms. Navigate the maze, uncover secrets, hidden puzzles, and new mechanics. There is no need to use items in this game. Please refrain from touching anything. Any rumors of a wandering presence are greatly exaggerated.</p>",
